        $N的脖子用力一拉，呵－－！整条舌头都伸出来啦！狱卒再手起刀落哗－－！ 
        整个世界清净了。\n"NOR,ob); 
        //ob->unconcious(); 
        ob->skill_death_penalty(); 
        ob->skill_death_penalty(); 
        ob->skill_death_penalty(); 
        ob->skill_death_penalty(); 
        ob->skill_death_penalty(); 
         //this_object()->move(CT)
;
        ob->move(place);
        return; 
} 
